# sonoUno-lhc

## Installation

```bash
pip install sonouno-lhc
```

## Run the data sample

```bash
python -m sonouno_lhc
```

## Inspect results

```bash
mplayer sonouno-lhc-outputs/sound-dataset-326146241.wav
eog sonouno-lhc-outputs/plot-dataset-326146241.png
```
